# Deployment

## Frontend: Vercel

- **Site:** https://npc-am.com
- **Hosting:** Vercel
- **Deploy:** Git push to `master` triggers automatic build on Vercel. API routes at `/api/morning`, `/api/morning-save-credentials`.
- **Ignore:** Netlify deployment scripts, `netlify.toml`, `netlify/` folder.

## When user says "deploy"

- **Frontend:** `git push origin master` — Vercel builds and deploys automatically.
- **Supabase Edge Functions:** `npx supabase functions deploy <function-name>` (e.g. `send-email`, `calendar-invite`).
